In Volatile Markets Do Analysts Think You Should Buy China Telecom Corp Ltd (NYSE:CHA)?


 By Ashley Brown /  in  Stocks /  on  Thursday, 13 Jul 2017 06:20 AM  / 0 Comments




Following U.S. election volatility some analysts have updated their recommended target prices on shares of China Telecom Corp Ltd (NYSE:CHA).  	 According to the most recently released broker notes, 2 analysts have a rating of “strong buy” on the stock, 0 analysts “buy”, 0 analysts “neutral”, 0 analysts “sell” and 0 analysts “strong sell”. 	  



